Hi all,
I made a new profile and canonical url is "http://example.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/MyObservation_jeff".
I tested my resource with this profile via "vonk.fire.ly" .
But, it said "Unable to resolve reference to profile 'http://example.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/MyObservation_jeff'"
Is there any way to give the right canonical url of this profile ?

Thanks !!
Hi Jeff, I think I answered this question here already: http://community.fhir.org/t/how-to-make-resource-json-with-new-profile/1777/3 ?
